rows.label: qst200810_msg0101
rows.name:
Oh, it looks like you got us the
Healing Teak!

rows.label: qst200810_msg0102
rows.name:
We'll get started straight away.
Just wait there, okay?

rows.label: qst200810_msg0104
rows.name:
Right, it's done!
It should be able to brace any tree,
no matter how big!

rows.label: qst200810_msg0107
rows.name:
Yeah! It's a manufactured thing,
but it still looks like it's breathing,
growing...

rows.label: qst200810_msg0108
rows.name:
You've got a good eye, miss.
You can be sure we wouldn't just
want to kill a tree or plant!

rows.label: qst200810_msg0109
rows.name:
We just shape it so it can live
alongside us.

rows.label: qst200810_msg0110
rows.name:
Ah, but here we are still chatting,
while the Saffronia waits for your help!
